DD2 - V.#12 - #557 Comes to understand


Huo Yuhao sighed, „per­haps, we came back is a mis­take. We not only can­not di­vert the Sun-Moon Em­pire army, in­stead was di­verted by them in Shrek City. Can­not pose the threat to the Sun-Moon Em­pire na­tive place, as the mat­ter stands, our orig­i­nal strate­gies all be­came the bub­ble. More­over, Wu­tong said right, I be­lieve that by the Ju Zi(or­ange) wis­dom, will not place Shrek City the main ob­jec­tive of at­tack. At­tack­ing a for­ti­fied po­si­tion, but may also be at­tacks the two coun­tries whole-heart­edly sup­port the firm city, com­pelling Acad­emy to go all out, this is not the mat­ter that pre­sent Sun-Moon Em­pire should do.” 霍雨浩叹息一声,“或许,我们回来是个错误。我们不但没能将日月帝国大军牵制回去,反而被他们牵制在了史莱克城。再不能对日月帝国本土构成威胁,这样一来,我们原来的战略就全都成为泡影了。而且,舞桐说得对,我相信,以橘子的智慧,绝不会将主要攻击目标放在史莱克城。攻坚,还有可能是攻击两国全力以赴支持的坚城,逼学院拼命,这可不是现在日月帝国应该做的事。” „Sorry, Yuhao, I should not say, if you an­a­lyzes, can per­haps say obe­di­ence po­si­tion An­cient Elder.” Tang Wu­tong low­ers the head, seems like the child of wrong thing. “对不起,雨浩,我不该那么说,如果是你自己来分析的话,说不定能说服众位宿老。”唐舞桐低着头,就像是个做错事的孩子。 Huo Yuhao grips her hand, shook the head, said: „Does not blame you, even if me, the re­sult will not change. Ju Zi(or­ange) is re­ally fierce, this move of open in­trigue, com­pelling Acad­emy to help one­self, no one dares to make the gam­bling stake with the Acad­emy safety. This is she most as­tute place. Re­ally is quite fierce!” 霍雨浩握住她的手,摇了摇头,道:“不怪你,就算是我来说,结局也不会改变的。橘子真是厉害,这一招阳谋,逼得学院不得不自救,谁也不敢用学院的安危做赌注。这才是她最精明的地方。果然是好厉害啊！” Beibei said: „We can­not this way, if cer­tainly wants the means to deal, oth­er­wise, this time was per­haps dan­ger­ous.” 贝贝道:“那我们也不能就这样下去,一定要想办法应对,否则的话,这次恐怕就危险了。” Huo Yuhao nod­ded, said: „This, Wu­tong, you re­turns to Acad­emy, to Inner Court that side in­quired that a de­ploy­ment of next pre­sent Star Lou Em­pire, where has a look at Duke White Tiger as well as Star Lou Em­pire main force. First Se­nior Brother, we go back first are the Lit­tle Ya Teacher treat­ments, then I look for a Duke