is as far as pos­si­ble be­comes by one­self more for­mi­da­ble, in the cru­cial time, plays the role of re­verse war. I can be good, cer­tainly can be good.” “大局暂时就只能任由情况发展下去了。不真正出现结果,学院的诸位宿老是不可能改变策略的。斗灵、星罗两国,我也尽力了。现在就看他们自己如何决断。而我现在要做的,就是尽可能让自己变得更加强大,在关键的时刻,起到扭转战局的作用。我能行,一定能行。” Thought aloud spoke of here, Huo Yuhao gripped the tight dou­ble fist, dou­ble pupil slowly closed, the body also started to relax, within the body Soul Power nat­u­rally pasted. 自言自语的说到这里,霍雨浩攥紧双拳,双眸缓缓闭合,身体也开始放松,体内魂力自然流转起来。 Be­fore Tang Wu­tong, pro­posed Ul­ti­mate Sol­dier time, Huo Yuhao un­der­stood her mean­ing. His Soul Power card in 89 lev­els, can­not be­come Ti­tled Douluo even­tu­ally. From the strength, gen­eral Ti­tled Douluo is not his match. But re­gard­less of, re­gard­ing any Soul Mas­ter, be­comes the speed­ing up of Ti­tled Douluo strength enor­mous de­gree. Tal­ent higher Soul Mas­ter , to pro­mote is also big­ger. 唐舞桐之前提出极限单兵的时候,霍雨浩就明白了她的意思。他的魂力一直卡在89级,终究没能成为封号斗罗。从实力上来看,一般的封号斗罗绝不是他的对手。可是,无论对于任何魂师来说,成为封号斗罗实力都会极大程度的提高。天赋越高的魂师,提升的也就越大。 Let alone, Huo Yuhao had first Soul Nu­cleus, once his sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus con­denses suc­cess­fully, the Soul Power essence has not dis­tin­guished with Limit Douluo any­thing, in the fu­ture the rapid­ness of Soul Power wind­ing speed, will be hard to imag­ine. 更何况,霍雨浩已经拥有了第一魂核,一旦他第二魂核凝聚成功,魂力本质就和极限斗罗没什么区别了,未来魂力提升速度之快,是难以想象的。 Since these days, Huo Yuhao has been ac­cu­mu­lat­ing ac­tu­ally, ac­cu­mu­lated was very long. When he in the icy seas deep place, ob­tained one­self Spirit Eyes Mar­tial Soul eighth Soul Ring , after is own sixth spirit Mer­maid Princess, spir­i­tual sea once more qual­i­ta­tive change, Spir­i­tual Power sud­denly to in­crease. Later was af­fected by the plant, com­pre­hended more pro­found Minute Sub­tlety bound­ary. Pre­sent he, truly had has at­tacked the sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus pos­si­bil­ity. In the mind con­trol­ling force, he is not at least in­fe­rior in any 98 lev­els of Soul Mas­ter. 这段时间以来,霍雨浩其实一直都在积累,已经积累了很久。当他在冰海深处,获得了自己灵眸武魂的第八魂环,也是自己的第六个魂灵人鱼公主之后,精神之海再次质变,精神力暴增。之后又受到植物的影响,领悟了更深刻的入微境界。现在的他,确实是已经具备了冲击第二魂核的可能。至少在精神控制力上,他决不逊色于任何98级魂师。 Be­com­ing by one­self more for­mi­da­ble, can have many rights to speak, can have the change bat­tle­field abil­ity. This is place that Huo Yuhao thinks through. 让自己变得更加强大,才能拥有更多的话语权,才能拥有改变战场的能力。这就是霍雨浩想通的地方。 Al­though in­di­vid­ual strength is tiny, but, some­times, in­di­vid­ual can also skid the gen­eral sit­u­a­tion. Now can­not, pow­er­ful, per­haps was OK! Since does not have other good means now, then, strength­ens one­self is the best choice. 个人的力量虽然渺小,但是,在某些时候,个人也能够撬动大局。现在不能,实力强大了,或许就可以了！既然现在也没有其他好办法,那么,增强自身就是最好的选择。 Huo Yuhao has thought through, there­fore he de­cides to close up. 霍雨浩想通了,所以他决定闭关。 More­over, prac­tice way that he must carry on with the Tang Wu­tong imag­i­na­tion is dif­fer­ent. 而且,他要进行的修炼方式和唐舞桐想象中的还不一样。 It looks like in Tang Wu­tong, pre­sent he, cul­ti­vates own Soul Nu­cleus in the Equal Res­o­nance way is the best means. But, Huo Yuhao ac­tu­ally does not think. He knows that in the fu­ture must chal­lenge Beast God Di Tian such to exist. If in­fe­rior to Di Tian com­pletely, then, one­self achieve­ment pos­si­bly does not have. In this case, his only choice, walks with the Di Tian same road, even do him is bet­ter, is stronger than him. 在唐舞桐看来,现在的他,以同位共振的方式修炼自身魂核是最好的办法。可是,霍雨浩却不这么想。他知道,未来自己一定是要挑战兽神帝天那样存在的。如果在根本上就不如帝天,那么,自己就一点获胜的可能都没有。在这种情况下,他唯一的选择,就是走和帝天同样的路,甚至要比他做的更好,比他更强。 Thinks of here, Huo Yuhao has set firm re­solve, within the body Soul Power na­ture cir­cu­la­tion, the fore­head place, Soul Nu­cleus is sta­ble, Spir­i­tual Power is cen­tered on Soul Nu­cleus, is cir­cling sim­i­larly. 想到这里,霍雨浩已经下定决心,体内魂力自然流转,额头处,魂核稳定,精神力以魂核为中心,也同样盘旋着。 Huo Yuhao Soul Nu­cleus, is he now all strengths cen­ters, first around Soul Nu­cleus, is cir­cling is his Spir­i­tual Power, the sur­round­ing is Soul Power. 霍雨浩的魂核,就是他现在一切力量的中心,在魂核周围,首先盘旋着的就是他的精神力,外围才是魂力。 If ob­serves from spir­i­tual sea, will dis­cover that has a huge di­a­mond Sun in his spir­i­tual sea, this Sun, is his Soul Nu­cleus. His Spir­i­tual Power now is ex­is­tence of close solid state, but also as be­fore re­volves Soul Nu­cleus to cir­cle. 如果从精神之海去观察的话,就会发现,在他精神之海中有一颗巨大的菱形太阳,这颗太阳,就是他的魂核。他的精神力现在已经是接近固态的存在,但也依旧围绕着魂核盘旋着。 Huo Yuhao then must do, opens own sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus. 霍雨浩接下来要做的,就是开启自己的第二魂核。 Ac­cord­ing to Old Xuan, this first Soul Nu­cleus opens is not easy, but ac­tu­ally es­tab­lished sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus to open the rel­a­tively easy foun­da­tion, be­cause sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus in the dant­ian, the dant­ian stored up the Soul Power place, es­tab­lished Soul Nu­cleus be much eas­ier than in other places in the dant­ian. 按照玄老所说,他这第一魂核开启的不容易,但却奠定了第二魂核开启相对容易的基础,因为第二魂核在丹田之中,丹田本来就是储存魂力的地方,在丹田建立魂核就要比在其他地方容易得多。 But, Huo Yuhao after these days ac­cu­mu­lates, in the heart had other ideas. 可是,霍雨浩经过这段时间积累之后,心中却有了其他的想法。 The dant­ian opens Soul Nu­cleus is very no doubt good, is, not nec­es­sar­ily will be best re­gard­ing the de­vel­op­ment trend. 丹田开启魂核固然很好,可是,对于未来发展却未必是最佳的。 Be­cause he must choose, is not the Equal Res­o­nance prac­tice way, but must carry on the method of prac­tice Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment. 因为他要选择的,并不是同位共振的修炼方式,而是要进行阴阳互补之法修炼。 Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment, that is the pro and con goes against, prac­tice it­self for dif­fi­cult, once car­ries on the Soul Nu­cleus prac­tice by the dant­ian. First did not say suc­cess­fully, once he has suc­ceeded, then, in within the body two Soul Nu­cleus sur­round­ing strengths re­volve on the con­trary, each other haul­ing, each other is sup­ple­men­tary. From the dant­ian to be­tween the eye­brows, is Soul Power and Spir­i­tual Power rev­o­lu­tion place. 阴阳互补,那就是正反相逆,修炼本身即为困难,而一旦以丹田进行魂核修炼的话。先不说不成功,一旦他成功了,那么,体内两个魂核周围的力量相反运转,彼此牵引、彼此互补。从丹田到眉心,都是魂力和精神力运转的地方。 When then, later Huo Yuhao Soul Power is 98 lev­els of times what to do? 那么,等到以后霍雨浩魂力达到98级的时候怎么办？ Per­haps, at that time he had to com­pare fa­vor­ably with the Limit Douluo strength, but, that time he, ac­tu­ally as be­fore was not Limit Douluo! To break through to 99 lev­els, be­comes human Ab­solute, then, must be based on Soul Nu­cleus to break through. In other words, in the fu­ture Huo Yuhao must carry on the con­den­sa­tion of third Soul Nu­cleus. 或许,在那时候他已经拥有媲美极限斗罗的实力了,但是,那时候的他,却依旧不是极限斗罗啊！想要突破到99级,成为人类极致,那么,就必须要以魂核突破为基础。也就是说,未来霍雨浩还要进行第三魂核的凝聚。 As the mat­ter stands, if his first two Soul Nu­cleus oc­cu­pied in the Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment con­di­tion from the dant­ian to the be­tween the eye­brows com­plete place, where his third does Soul Nu­cleus open? 这样一来,如果他的前两个魂核已经在阴阳互补状态下占据了从丹田到眉心的全部地方,那他的第三魂核开启在什么地方？

