DD2 - V.#12 - #558 The masculine and feminine elements is supplementary, the second soul nucleus


Hu­man­ity has three places to open Soul Nu­cleus, be­tween the eye­brows, chest and dant­ian. To that time, has wanted be­tween the chest from two big Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment Soul Nu­cleus to open third Soul Nu­cleus again, sim­ply is dream of a fool. That needs to in­ter­rupt two big Soul Nu­cleus re­la­tions orig­i­nally to be good di­rectly first. In that case, Huo Yuhao di­rectly from ex­plod­ing. 人类只有三个地方可以开启魂核,眉心、胸口和丹田。到了那时候,再想从两大阴阳互补魂核之间的胸口开启第三魂核,简直是痴人说梦。那需要直接先打断两大魂核原本的联系才行。那样的话,霍雨浩自己就直接自爆了。 In other words, if Huo Yuhao chooses sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus opens in the dant­ian, then, he will not have con­densed the third Soul Nu­cleus pos­si­bil­ity in the fu­ture, even if for­mi­da­ble, has not be­come the Limit Douluo strength. In that case, he could not in­herit God of Emo­tion God Po­si­tion. 也就是说,霍雨浩如果选择将第二魂核开启在丹田,那么,未来他就没有凝聚第三魂核的可能了,就算再强大,也没有成为极限斗罗的实力。那样的话,他就继承不了情绪之神的神位。 There­fore, in the Huo Yuhao heart early some plans, he al­ready had de­cided that own sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus not only need by form open­ing of Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment, but also the open­ing po­si­tion is the chest, va­cates the dant­ian, as the mat­ter stands, he also will have in the fu­ture in the dant­ian opens the third Soul Nu­cleus pos­si­bil­ity. At that time, third Soul Nu­cleus must face likely only then the chest lo­cated the dis­tur­bance of Soul Nu­cleus. 因此,霍雨浩心中早有打算,他早就已经决定,自己的第二魂核不但要以阴阳互补的形式开启,而且开启的位置是胸口,空出丹田来,这样一来,未来他就还有在丹田开启第三魂核的可能。那时候,第三魂核要面对的很可能就只有胸口处魂核的干扰。 „Ice Em­peror, Ice Em­peror you in?” Huo Yuhao ini­ti­ated sum­mon in the heart. “冰帝,冰帝你在吗？”霍雨浩在心中发起了呼唤。 „I, Yuhao, how?” Ice Em­peror sound along with it re­sound­ing. “我在,雨浩,怎么了？”冰帝的声音随之响起。 Huo Yuhao said: „I pre­pare to start to prac­tice my sec­ond Soul Nu­cleus, thus at­tacks the Ti­tled Douluo bound­ary. I must prac­tice in the Yin-Yang Sup­ple­ment way. Must trou­ble you to help me. Be­cause I must es­tab­lish Soul Nu­cleus in the chest place. My within the body fused your Ice Jade Em­peror Scor­pion Torso Bone, your