years, the Huo Yuhao abil­ity has been grow­ing, is Day­dream Ice Silk­worm looks that he walks step by step. There­fore, Brother Day­dream is nat­u­rally fa­mil­iar with his sit­u­a­tion. 霍雨浩当初碰到天梦冰蚕,天梦冰蚕和他进行融合,成为他的第一魂环。那时候,霍雨浩还像是一张白纸。这些年,霍雨浩的能力一直在成长,也是天梦冰蚕看着他一步步走过来的。所以,天梦哥对他的情况自然是再熟悉不过了。 Does not need Snow Em­peror to tell that Brother Day­dream has han­dled the most cor­rect mat­ter, trans­fers Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power, has blocked his own mind Soul Nu­cleus and com­mu­ni­ca­tion of out­side heaven and earth el­e­men­tal en­ergy. As the mat­ter stands, will not have heaven and earth el­e­men­tal en­ergy to enter around Soul Nu­cleus, formed Soul Power. 根本不需要雪帝吩咐,天梦哥已经做了最正确的事情,调动霍雨浩的精神力,封锁了他自身精神魂核与外界天地元力的沟通。这样一来,就不会有天地元力进入魂核周围,重新形成魂力了。 Spir­i­tual Power that mind Soul Nu­cleus re­leases out­ward will strengthen nat­u­rally, the re­sis­tance of out­side also sim­i­larly is the power that pro­motes it to re­volve. 精神魂核向外释放出的精神力自然而然会加强,外界的阻力也同样是促进它运转的动力。 Li Ya also moved at this time, gen­tle Spir­i­tual Power re­volves Soul Nu­cleus, slows down the speed of Soul Nu­cleus rev­o­lu­tion, car­ries on cer­tain sup­pres­sion. 丽雅也在这个时候动了,柔和的精神力围绕着魂核,减缓魂核运转的速度,对它进行一定的压制。 But Huo Yuhao as far as pos­si­ble speeds up Soul Power that re­as­signs in Soul Nu­cleus to com­press. 而霍雨浩则是尽可能的加快抽调魂核内压缩的魂力。 The re­bound of Soul Nu­cleus re­as­signs Soul Power to sur­pass 70% after Huo Yuhao started. The for­mi­da­ble suc­tion made Day­dream Ice Silk­worm arrange out­side mind bar­rier starts to drag, but Li Ya was con­trol­ling with every ef­fort, but also made this suc­tion pro­duce was slightly slow. 魂核的反弹从霍雨浩抽调魂力超过七成之后开始了。强大的吸力令天梦冰蚕布置在外面的精神屏障开始摇曳,而丽雅虽然在尽力控制,但也只是让这份吸力产生的略微慢一点而已。 This is the great strength of Soul Nu­cleus! Once Soul Nu­cleus forms, is the foun­tain­heads of Soul Mas­ter all strengths, so is can it be that easy to vac­il­late? 这就是魂核的强大！魂核一旦形成,就是魂师一切力量的源泉,又岂是那么容易动摇的？ The Huo Yuhao will is quite firm, al­though feels this change, does not have the mean­ing that any