还没有什么动静,只是冰帝不断控制着冰碧帝皇蝎躯干骨,吸收霍雨浩转移过来的魂力。 At this time, the great strength of Ice Jade Em­peror Scor­pion Torso Bone ap­peared, from start to the pre­sent, it has al­most ab­sorbed Huo Yuhao 50% Soul Power, as be­fore has not ac­tu­ally ar­rived at end. It­self be­comes lush green, has not made Huo Yuhao feel slightly full. 这个时候,冰碧帝皇蝎躯干骨的强大就显现出来了,从开始到现在,它几乎已经吸收了霍雨浩五成的魂力,却依旧没有到尽头似的。本身只是变得更加青翠欲滴,却丝毫没有让霍雨浩感觉到饱胀。 Process Huo Yuhao that the help of six big spir­its, at least this just started felt that is quite re­laxed. At pre­sent has not come across the dif­fi­cult prob­lem. 有六大魂灵的帮助,至少这刚开始的过程霍雨浩感觉到还是较为轻松的。目前还没遇到难题。 Soul Power ab­sorp­tion many of more and more, ter­ri­fy­ing Soul Power fluc­tu­ates every time to trem­ble, Huo Yuhao Soul Nu­cleus will be­come the even more wild sev­eral points. Li Ya deals started be­comes dif­fi­cult. To con­trol mind Soul Nu­cleus, quite in the Huo Yuhao for­mi­da­ble Spir­i­tual Power re­sis­tance. 魂力吸收的越来越多,恐怖的魂力波动每一次震颤,霍雨浩的魂核都会变得越发狂暴几分。丽雅应对的已经开始变得困难了。想要控制精神魂核,就相当于更霍雨浩强大的精神力对抗。 „Yuhao, con­trols Soul Nu­cleus, mak­ing him slow.” Snow Em­peror said. “雨浩,控制魂核,让他慢下来。”雪帝说道。 The Huo Yuhao thought moves, own mind Soul Nu­cleus re­stores im­me­di­ately under one­self con­trol. En­tire Soul Nu­cleus wild be­came has also sta­bi­lized. 霍雨浩意念一动,自己的精神魂核立刻恢复在自己掌控之下。整个魂核的狂暴也变得稳定了下来。 Li Ya was lib­er­ated im­me­di­ately, rests in his spir­i­tual sea. But has con­trolled mind Soul Nu­cleus Huo Yuhao, now can­not di­vert at­ten­tion to re­as­sign own Soul Power again. 丽雅立刻被解放了出来,在他的精神之海中休息。而控制了精神魂核的霍雨浩,现在就不能再分心去抽调自己的魂力了。 He is sup­press­ing the Soul Nu­cleus in­stinct now. The Soul Nu­cleus in­stinct sup­pressed re­sult, will make the re­bound more in­tense. 他现在是在抑制魂核的本能。魂核本能被抑制的结果,就会让反弹变得更加强烈。 A pow­er­ful suc­tion trans­mits from the dant­ian po­si­tion, pulls out to Huo Yuhao Soul Nu­cleus around final Ab­solute Ice Soul Power. This strength nat­u­rally from Snow Em­peror, she fi­nally got rid. 一股强盛的吸力从丹田位置传来,抽离霍雨浩魂核周围最后的极致之冰魂力。这股力量自然是来自于雪帝的,她终于